      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        A single, unified platform covering every inch of your operations: From <strong>Member Onboarding</strong> to <strong>Financial Reporting</strong>, <strong>CRB Listing</strong>, and <strong>Mobile Banking</strong>.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 mb-16">
        <a href="#member-mgt" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/30">
          View Full Feature List
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-slate-900 border border-slate-200 px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
          Download Brochure
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto border-t border-slate-200 pt-10">
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">BOSA & FOSA</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">Fully Integrated</div></div>
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">SASRA Reports</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">Automated</div></div>
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">M-Pesa</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">C2B & B2C</div></div>
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">Cloud Based</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">Access Anywhere</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="sticky top-[72px] z-40 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border-y border-slate-200 py-4 hidden md:block">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 flex justify-center gap-8 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">
      <a href="#member-mgt" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Membership</a>
      <a href="#bosa" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">BOSA / Loans</a>
      <a href="#fosa" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">FOSA / Banking</a>
