        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-8">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">Registration & KYC</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Capture Bio-data, Next of Kin, Beneficiaries.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> IPRS Integration (Validate ID numbers automatically).</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Assign Member Numbers (Auto-increment or Custom).</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Manage Joining Fees & Share Capital requirements.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">Group/Chama Management</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Register Groups, Corporates, and Joint Accounts.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Track individual members within a group.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Group Loan Products & Co-guaranteeing logic.</li>
