              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Log complaints and support tickets per member.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">Exits & Re-admission</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Manage resignation notices (60 days logic).</li>
