              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Product Config:</strong> Define Interest Rates, Repayment Period, Calculation Method (Reducing/Straight Line/Amortized).</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Appraisal:</strong> Auto-check 1/3rd rule, x3 or x4 deposits multiplier.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Disbursement:</strong> Pay via Cheque, EFT, or M-Pesa B2C.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Top-ups/Refinancing:</strong> Bridge existing loans with auto-deduction of balance and bridging fees.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-4">Guarantor Management</h4>
