              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Validation:</strong> Ensure guarantor has enough free shares.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Witnessing:</strong> SMS OTP validation for guarantors.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Asset Collateral:</strong> Register Logbooks/Title Deeds as security.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Substitution:</strong> Formal process to replace guarantors.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-4">Shares & Deposits</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Minimum Contributions:</strong> Auto-penalty for missed monthly savings.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Share Capital:</strong> Manage transfer of non-withdrawable capital.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Statements:</strong> Generate detailed BOSA statements.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-4">Dividends & Rebates</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Auto-Calculation:</strong> Based on pro-rata duration of deposits.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Withholding Tax:</strong> Auto-deduct 5% WHT for KRA.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Capitalization:</strong> Allow members to capitalize dividends to shares.</li>
